        <p style="font-size: 14px; min-height:  125px"><a href="#earth-pulse" style="text-decoration: none;">The Earth Pulse is a glimmering chandelier-like sculpture that visualizes live communication with NASA’s Earth satellites, using light activity that represents data transmission in real time. Different patterns and speeds represent the amount of data being transferred and how quickly it reaches its destination.</a></p><a href="#earth-pulse">
